( yells )

11:25.417 --> 11:26.667
( sighs of relief )

11:28.542 --> 11:30.875
(  solemn theme plays  )

11:42.625 --> 11:45.458
Since when does Optimus

11:42.625 --> 11:45.458
have a caboose?

11:47.709 --> 11:49.000
Greetings,

11:47.709 --> 11:49.000
Rescue Bots.

11:49.041 --> 11:50.709
Nice rig.

11:50.750 --> 11:54.583
The Transport is for carrying

11:50.750 --> 11:54.583
Energon to the surface,

11:54.625 --> 11:58.291
once the Rescue Bots and I

11:54.625 --> 11:58.291
harvest it from underground.

11:58.333 --> 12:00.583
We'd like to help you

11:58.333 --> 12:00.583
if we can.

12:00.625 --> 12:04.208
I do not wish to endanger

12:00.625 --> 12:04.208
your family, Chief.

12:04.250 --> 12:06.667
Great. Yet another trip to the

12:04.250 --> 12:06.667
center of the Earth

12:06.709 --> 12:08.458
we won't be making.

12:08.500 --> 12:12.041
But we will require the

12:08.500 --> 12:12.041
coordinates your brother found.

12:12.083 --> 12:14.417
Yeah...

12:12.083 --> 12:14.417
A bit of a problem.

12:14.458 --> 12:16.959
Woodrow's kind of...

12:14.458 --> 12:16.959
disappeared.

12:17.000 --> 12:18.417
BOULDER:

12:17.000 --> 12:18.417
Heatwave! Chief!

12:19.667 --> 12:22.041
Optimus,

12:19.667 --> 12:22.041
thank goodness.

12:22.083 --> 12:24.583
Chief,

12:22.083 --> 12:24.583
Cody and your brother...

12:24.625 --> 12:26.875
The Forger took off tunneling,

12:24.625 --> 12:26.875
with them inside!

12:26.917 --> 12:28.208
Then let's roll to the--

12:28.250 --> 12:29.542
We'd never reach it,

12:28.250 --> 12:29.542
Heatwave.

12:29.583 --> 12:31.000
It has too much

12:29.583 --> 12:31.000
of a head start.

12:31.041 --> 12:34.291
It appears our

12:31.041 --> 12:34.291
mining expedition is now

12:34.333 --> 12:35.959
a rescue mission.

12:36.000 --> 12:38.083
For the entire team.

12:39.542 --> 12:41.709
Rescue Bots...

12:39.542 --> 12:41.709
vehicle mode,

12:41.750 --> 12:43.834
then on to my transport.

12:43.875 --> 12:46.917
No offense, Optimus,

12:43.875 --> 12:46.917
but how can you pulling us

12:46.959 --> 12:49.417
on a trailer be any faster

12:46.959 --> 12:49.417
than going ourselves?

12:49.458 --> 12:53.166
Let's just say

12:49.458 --> 12:53.166
there is more to this transport

12:53.208 --> 12:54.875
than meets the eye.

12:55.917 --> 12:57.583
(  heroic theme plays  )

13:05.166 --> 13:07.625
We're nearing the coordinates.

13:05.166 --> 13:07.625
We should be leveling off.

13:16.041 --> 13:17.667
Oh,

13:16.041 --> 13:17.667
the controls aren't working!

13:17.709 --> 13:19.792
( beeping )

13:19.834 --> 13:22.583
My brothers are always telling

13:19.834 --> 13:22.583
me not to press strange buttons,

13:22.625 --> 13:23.917
but I think that might be--

13:23.959 --> 13:25.875
The kill button.

13:23.959 --> 13:25.875
Go for it!

13:30.375 --> 13:32.750
( both yelp )

13:32.792 --> 13:34.959
CODY:

13:32.792 --> 13:34.959
Get out, Uncle Woodrow,

13:32.792 --> 13:34.959
before we're buried.

13:36.250 --> 13:37.750
( struggling )

13:44.291 --> 13:46.417
(  mysterious theme plays  )

13:52.458 --> 13:54.375
(  triumphant theme plays  )

13:54.417 --> 13:56.917
Whoa! Noble!

13:56.959 --> 13:58.000
( laughs )

13:58.041 --> 14:00.458
Whatever that means,

13:58.041 --> 14:00.458
I agree.

14:02.083 --> 14:04.667
This looks like the place your

14:02.083 --> 14:04.667
DES photographed.

14:05.667 --> 14:07.417
Yup.

14:07.458 --> 14:10.583
We're smack dab where we're

14:07.458 --> 14:10.583
supposed to be.

14:10.625 --> 14:11.959
But...

14:12.000 --> 14:13.291
no way back.

14:13.333 --> 14:15.417
My dad will launch a

14:13.333 --> 14:15.417
rescue mission.

14:15.458 --> 14:17.041
He probably already has.

14:17.083 --> 14:20.083
Cody, no one even knows

14:17.083 --> 14:20.083
we're down here.

14:20.125 --> 14:22.875
Who's gonna tell them?

14:20.125 --> 14:22.875
Your bulldozer?

14:28.834 --> 14:30.166
OPTIMUS:

14:28.834 --> 14:30.166
Chief Burns,

14:30.208 --> 14:32.959
I suggest you and your family

14:30.208 --> 14:32.959
hold onto something.

14:33.000 --> 14:34.000
What?

14:37.083 --> 14:38.625
( all scream )

14:40.625 --> 14:41.917
Is he crazy?

14:41.959 --> 14:44.250
He's Optimus Prime.

14:41.959 --> 14:44.250
Relax.

14:48.709 --> 14:50.166
Statistically speaking,

14:50.208 --> 14:51.792
that maneuver should not

14:50.208 --> 14:51.792
have worked.

14:58.542 --> 15:00.166
Uncle Woodrow,

14:58.542 --> 15:00.166
over here.

15:00.208 --> 15:01.959
Huh...

15:02.000 --> 15:05.959
Must be the tunnel the DES dug

15:02.000 --> 15:05.959
on its exploratory mission.

15:06.000 --> 15:08.542
So it should lead to the

15:06.000 --> 15:08.542
surface, right?

15:08.583 --> 15:11.583
Even if we could reach it,

15:08.583 --> 15:11.583
it's too small to fit through.

15:13.417 --> 15:14.750
Wait...

15:16.667 --> 15:18.333
I've seen that before.

15:19.709 --> 15:20.667
( beeps )

15:20.709 --> 15:22.166
The alien housing structure.

15:23.166 --> 15:25.083
Oh,

15:23.166 --> 15:25.083
your dad was right.

15:25.125 --> 15:27.709
It's just

15:25.125 --> 15:27.709
a rock formation.

15:27.750 --> 15:29.417
( echoes )

15:32.083 --> 15:35.000
And there's my alien

15:32.083 --> 15:35.000
communication signal.

15:35.041 --> 15:36.792
Uncle Woodrow,

15:36.834 --> 15:38.834
that doesn't mean

15:36.834 --> 15:38.834
we won't find other proof.

15:38.875 --> 15:40.166
You never know,

15:40.208 --> 15:41.834
there just might be aliens

15:40.208 --> 15:41.834
after all.

15:41.875 --> 15:43.750
( scoffs )

15:41.875 --> 15:43.750
Yeah.

15:43.792 --> 15:46.125
( distant chittering )

15:47.917 --> 15:49.917
They found us!

15:47.917 --> 15:49.917
I told you they would.

15:49.959 --> 15:51.834
(  triumphant theme plays  )

15:51.875 --> 15:53.834
( chittering continues )

15:53.875 --> 15:56.083
I'm not so sure.

15:56.125 --> 15:57.417
( chittering grows louder )

15:57.458 --> 15:59.458
(  theme turns threatening  )

16:04.458 --> 16:06.208
( loud chittering )

16:10.500 --> 16:11.917
( growling )

16:11.959 --> 16:13.458
( rumbling )

16:14.709 --> 16:16.542
(  heroic theme plays  )

16:25.458 --> 16:27.375
( whispers )

16:25.458 --> 16:27.375
Scorpions!

16:27.417 --> 16:28.709
No.

16:28.750 --> 16:30.041
Much worse.

16:30.083 --> 16:31.750
(  dramatic theme plays  )

16:39.166 --> 16:40.583
( grunting and yelping )

16:42.667 --> 16:44.208
That new robot...

16:44.250 --> 16:45.750
Impressive!

16:50.667 --> 16:52.000
( yelps )

16:54.500 --> 16:55.834
Dad!

16:57.458 --> 16:59.375
( Woodrow and Cody struggle )

17:00.417 --> 17:02.417
(  tense theme plays  )

17:12.583 --> 17:14.959
(  triumphant theme plays  )

17:15.000 --> 17:16.458
Herd 'em this way!

17:19.417 --> 17:21.458
( grunting )

17:35.625 --> 17:37.375
(  heroic theme plays  )

17:43.250 --> 17:45.208
Oh, Cody...

17:45.250 --> 17:47.458
What on Earth

17:45.250 --> 17:47.458
were you thinking?

17:47.500 --> 17:49.375
Didn't I tell you--?

17:47.500 --> 17:49.375
It wasn't his fault, Dad.

17:49.417 --> 17:50.709
The Forger just took off and--

17:50.750 --> 17:53.000
No, Cody.

17:50.750 --> 17:53.000
Your dad's right.

17:53.041 --> 17:56.750
It's my fault for sneaking off

17:53.041 --> 17:56.750
on this goose chase.

17:56.792 --> 17:59.458
I put you in danger,

17:56.792 --> 17:59.458
and I'm sorry for that.

17:59.500 --> 18:01.542
Thank you,

17:59.500 --> 18:01.542
Woodrow.

18:01.583 --> 18:02.875
Apology accepted.

18:02.917 --> 18:04.709
The worst part is...

18:04.750 --> 18:07.000
the entire trip was pointless.

18:07.041 --> 18:10.375
No lost civilization,

18:07.041 --> 18:10.375
no signs of alien life.

18:11.417 --> 18:13.125
You're right, Charlie.

18:13.166 --> 18:16.792
I've wasted my whole life just

18:13.166 --> 18:16.792
chasing...shadows.

18:16.834 --> 18:18.750
As soon as we get

18:16.834 --> 18:18.750
to the surface,

18:18.792 --> 18:20.291
I'll head home.

18:20.333 --> 18:22.542
And get out

18:20.333 --> 18:22.542
of your family's hair.

18:22.583 --> 18:24.500
( whispering ):

18:22.583 --> 18:24.500
Why is he talking about hair?

18:24.542 --> 18:27.500
( whispering )

18:24.542 --> 18:27.500
A metaphor. I'll explain later.

18:27.542 --> 18:29.834
But Uncle Woodrow...

18:27.542 --> 18:29.834
what are you going to do?

18:29.875 --> 18:33.083
I'm not sure.

18:29.875 --> 18:33.083
But I have to face it.

18:33.125 --> 18:35.000
Atlantis,

18:33.125 --> 18:35.000
Shangri La...

18:35.041 --> 18:36.500
no such things.

18:36.542 --> 18:38.709
And aliens have never visited

18:36.542 --> 18:38.709
because they don't exist.

18:41.917 --> 18:44.083
What?

18:41.917 --> 18:44.083
He is family, Dad.

18:44.125 --> 18:46.458
You can't let him go on

18:44.125 --> 18:46.458
thinking he's failed.

18:46.500 --> 18:48.834
I mean if it were Kade,

18:46.500 --> 18:48.834
I'd try to cheer him up.

18:48.875 --> 18:50.208
Maybe.

18:50.250 --> 18:51.959
Tell him,

18:50.250 --> 18:51.959
Dad!

18:52.000 --> 18:53.250
Tell me what?

18:57.875 --> 19:00.125
Woodrow...little brother.

19:00.166 --> 19:02.917
I don't know about Shangri-La,

19:00.166 --> 19:02.917
or Atlantis,

19:02.959 --> 19:07.166
but I can tell you as a point of

19:02.959 --> 19:07.166
fact... aliens do exist.

19:07.208 --> 19:08.208
( sighs )

19:08.250 --> 19:10.083
You don't have to do this,

19:08.250 --> 19:10.083
Charlie.

19:10.125 --> 19:11.875
It doesn't make me feel

19:10.125 --> 19:11.875
any better.

19:11.917 --> 19:13.959
Well maybe this will.

19:14.000 --> 19:16.250
Team,

19:14.000 --> 19:16.250
introduce yourselves.

19:16.291 --> 19:18.667
Heatwave.

19:16.291 --> 19:18.667
Pleased to meet you.

19:18.709 --> 19:20.542
My name is Chase.

19:20.583 --> 19:22.792
And I am proud to be your

19:20.583 --> 19:22.792
brother's policing partner.

19:22.834 --> 19:24.458
Boulder.

19:24.500 --> 19:25.792
Blades.

19:25.834 --> 19:27.417
And now that I

19:25.834 --> 19:27.417
can speak freely,

19:27.458 --> 19:30.792
can I just say how terrifying

19:27.458 --> 19:30.792
those spiders were?

19:30.834 --> 19:32.333
Not gonna fall for it.

19:34.834 --> 19:38.959
I am Optimus Prime.

19:34.834 --> 19:38.959
And Chief Burns is correct.

19:39.000 --> 19:41.625
To the people of Earth,

19:39.000 --> 19:41.625
we are aliens.

19:41.667 --> 19:46.041
Our home planet of Cybertron

19:41.667 --> 19:46.041
is most likely unknown to you.

19:46.083 --> 19:48.291
We'd tell you

19:46.083 --> 19:48.291
what galaxy it's in,

19:48.333 --> 19:49.875
but you haven't heard of that,

19:48.333 --> 19:49.875
either.

19:49.917 --> 19:54.333
I was right.

19:49.917 --> 19:54.333
I was right!

19:54.375 --> 19:56.542
( laughs )

19:54.375 --> 19:56.542
I just...I just...

19:56.583 --> 19:58.959
My DES worked,

19:56.583 --> 19:58.959
Charlie...

19:59.000 --> 20:01.208
it found aliens!

20:01.250 --> 20:03.583
I just never figured you'd be

20:01.250 --> 20:03.583
the one hiding them.

20:03.625 --> 20:05.709
So...

20:05.750 --> 20:07.500
you guys...

20:07.542 --> 20:08.792
Cybernites!

20:08.834 --> 20:10.792
Cybertronians.

20:10.834 --> 20:13.583
Right. You've been leaving

20:10.834 --> 20:13.583
artifacts on Earth?

20:13.625 --> 20:14.959
For what,

20:13.625 --> 20:14.959
like centuries?

20:15.000 --> 20:19.000
That is a long story,

20:15.000 --> 20:19.000
for another day.

20:19.041 --> 20:21.083
Oh, I knew it!

20:21.125 --> 20:24.291
Wow, thanks, Charlie. For

20:21.125 --> 20:24.291
trusting me with your secret.

20:24.333 --> 20:27.458
Like Graham said,

20:24.333 --> 20:27.458
we're all family.

20:27.500 --> 20:30.166
And that's

20:27.500 --> 20:30.166
what family does.

20:30.208 --> 20:31.583
They also do this...

20:32.792 --> 20:34.000
Ha-ha-ha!

20:32.792 --> 20:34.000
Hey!

20:34.041 --> 20:35.709
Stop it, Charlie!

20:35.750 --> 20:39.083
This gesture appears to be

20:35.750 --> 20:39.083
universal in sibling relations.

20:39.125 --> 20:42.208
Let's get to work team.

20:39.125 --> 20:42.208
We have some Energon to harvest.

20:42.250 --> 20:44.000
( rumbling )

20:44.041 --> 20:45.917
(  tense theme plays  )

20:46.709 --> 20:47.667
( all exclaim )

20:47.709 --> 20:48.959
CHIEF:

20:47.709 --> 20:48.959
Everybody,

20:47.709 --> 20:48.959
watch it!

21:05.083 --> 21:06.625
( yells )

21:06.667 --> 21:08.542
( grunting )

21:13.709 --> 21:15.083
CHIEF:

21:13.709 --> 21:15.083
This way!

21:19.375 --> 21:20.667
( both yell )

21:20.709 --> 21:22.000
CODY:

21:20.709 --> 21:22.000
Heatwave!

21:22.041 --> 21:23.709
CHIEF:

21:22.041 --> 21:23.709
Cody, come on!

